metadata.name: Roo Rap #1/83
metadata.description:
The first track released by DCoop & Patty Mack for the Roo Troop community. Rooty MF Roo! Mp3 music file available to claim! To claim your mp3 verify that you hold the Roo Rap at https://roorap.orvylle.xyz/. Minters will be entered into our exclusive NFT giveaway/s the next one being on 2/23 @ 10:00 pm EST make sure to follow @dcoopofficial on Twitter to stay up to date! Minters will have exclusive access to all future tracks & projects by both DCoop & Patty Mack! If you want to really Roo it up and join in on our future burn mechanism it's 3 to burn 4 to HODL.

Allocation of funds: 33% Domestic Violence Donation (we will provide announcements on this), 33% Reinvested, 33% for sweeping NFTs, giveaways, and community holdings - the more minted the more we sweep and give away. The funds will be sent to villagentertainmentcollective.eth (for reinvestment and sweeps) and the 33% for Domestic Violence will then be sent to defiantdames.eth at the 24 hour mark for the end of presale and the 72 hour mark for the finish of public.
